(2, 1, '2017-12-07 16:00:10', '2017-12-07 13:00:10', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][rev_slider alias="home _page_slider"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="62" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Я текстовый блок. Нажмите кнопку редактирования, чтобы изменить этот текст. Разнообразный и богатый опыт постоянный количественный рост и сфера нашей активности требуют от нас анализа позиций.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Я текстовый блок. Нажмите кнопку редактирования, чтобы изменить этот текст. Разнообразный и богатый опыт постоянный количественный рост и сфера нашей активности требуют от нас анализа позиций.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="66" img_size="medium"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][wcs-schedule id=1][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text][wcs-schedule id=1][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text][fts_twitter twitter_name=INBalletConserv tweets_count=4 twitter_height=700px cover_photo=no stats_bar=no show_retweets=no show_replies=no][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>IBCSI 2017: June 26 th -July 28 th , 2017</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>3 options for enrollment – 1 st two weeks, last 3 weeks, or all 5 weeks </strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>*Last 3 weeks required for students wishing to perform in the Gala</strong></em></p>\nIBC’s Summer Intensive is a comprehensive five-week program designed to give serious students a well-rounded dance education and exposure to the Vaganova- based curriculum provided by IBC. Taught by our world-class instructors in a professional atmosphere, the IBCSI will allow students to experience the training that has consistently won awards and recognition in the ballet world. Now in its 7 th year, the IBCSI has quickly grown into one of the most well-regarded and sought- after summer programs for career-minded students.\n\nWith well over 30 hours per week of training and focused attention on individual needs, IBCSI provides each student a greater opportunity to grow and improve. Students receive the highest level of training by our esteemed Faculty:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Alyona Yakovleva-Randall, Founding Artistic Director</li>\n 	<li>Tatiana Pali, Academy Principal and Ballet Mistress</li>\n 	<li>Sergey Sergiev, Contemporary Instructor &amp;amp; Choreographer</li>\n 	<li>as well as others, plus Master Classes by leading professionals in the ballet world</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_video link="https://youtu.be/xjr4KlFGVpo"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_video link="https://youtu.be/aYrBQQ-FSRI"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_video link="https://youtu.be/EunyqqXlRTY"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2017-12-11 17:13:52', '2017-12-11 14:13:52', '', 0, 'http://ibc.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
